{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"41b1886456","title":"陈再道对武汉造反派的讲话记要","origin":"打倒反革命修正主义分子——陈再道》　武汉钢二司武汉大学总部宣传部　毛泽东思想武汉军区政治部红旗总部合编　河南二七公社宣传部翻印　1967年9月","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7a7d3c623c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":11,"articleId":"41b1886456"}],"tags":[{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4d9a2ea656","name":"陈再道","type":"人物"},{"id":"70a1e48626","name":"军队支左","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"6947f9d5e2","name":"陈再道"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"93c5d2e1c0","type":"title","text":"陈再道对武汉造反派的讲话记要","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b1886456"},{"id":"79dcacbb24","type":"authors","text":"陈再道","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b1886456"},{"id":"c6b658539b","type":"paragraph","text":"〖在武汉军区副司令孔庆德接见造反派的大会上，陈再道讲了话。下为记要。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b1886456"},{"id":"7f79239194","type":"paragraph","text":"1、你们是革命左派，（指新华工、新湖大、二司、三司），我们坚决依靠你们。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b1886456"},{"id":"867968e77b","type":"paragraph","text":"2、三字兵你们要作分化瓦解工作。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b1886456"},{"id":"bd799b4d34","type":"paragraph","text":"3、我们支持三字兵是错误的。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b1886456"},{"id":"1b504aac7f","type":"paragraph","text":"4、我们有缺点有错误，通过内部解决，以后见行动。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b1886456"},{"id":"3f578c34b6","type":"paragraph","text":"5、江青同志意见，成立支左监督小组。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b1886456"},{"id":"33916051ba","type":"paragraph","text":"《湖北日报》成立监督小组，（新华工两人、新湖大、二司、三司、新华农各一人）登造反派文章，树立你们的威信。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"41b1886456"},{"id":"74daccaf04","type":"paragraph","text":"7、要彻底批判刘少奇，王任重是当地最大的走资本主义道路的当权派。连同其《龚同文》一起批判。","inde